Mitsubishi Heavy Has No Plans to Agree to Hitachi Business Merger Talks

-- B y   K y u n g   B o k   C h o
-- 
2011-08-04T00:10:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/mitsubishi-heavy-has-no-plans-to-agree-to-hitachi-business-merger-talks.html
Mitsubishi Heavy Industries Ltd. (7011)  has
no plans to agree to a merger of some businesses with  Hitachi
Ltd. (6501) , according to a statement to the Tokyo Stock Exchange
today.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kyung Bok Cho at 
